o-timeusediary MPIAE Changes
============================


Current WIP
-----------
* NEW: support display_name property for days in cfg file, database and API


Version 0.6.2 -- Fix Editing template activities
-----------------------------------------------
* FIX: do not use ID of source activity when sending template activity, compute startTime and endTime for backend activities properly in frontend. Fixes bug in frontend that one cannot change times of activities.
* compute ISO format start_time and end_time in ISO time format like 08:30:00 from the minutes after midnight in backend and send with activites. a service for the frontend.
* add lots of dev scripts to repo that make it easier to test under conditions closer to production (nginx with reverse proxy setup, fastapi rootpath)


Version 0.6.1 -- Support display_name for days
------------------------------------------------
* NEW: support display_name property for days in cfg file, database and API


Version 0.6.0 -- Save and send activity category field
-------------------------------------------------------
* NEW: Save category field for activities when frontend sends data
* BRK: New category field for activity in database will require db migration or re-creation



Version 0.5.1 -- Startup bug fix
---------------------------------
* FIX: more robust creation of db tables during startup, required with multi-threaded WSGI server
* NEW: add template for Linux system service file


Version 0.5.0 -- First deployed version
---------------------------------------
* NEW: support rootpath setting for FastAPI
* NEW: support saving color of activities in database
* NEW: report version on startup


Version 0.4.1 -- admin infrastructure
---------------------------------------
* BRK: unify endpoints for getting activities from database by index vs by name into one
* NEW: adapt activities in cfg
* NEW: add endpoints to get study info
* NEW: validate many settings, both in cfg file and on API usage
* NEW: add admin pages


Version 0.4.0 -- Backend save data support
------------------------------------------
* NEW: API endpoint to send data to backend works and saves
* NEW: add data retrieval endpoint
* FIX: move various global setting to study-specific settings


Version 0.3.0 -- Fix case mismatch frontend - backend
------------------------------------------------------
* FIX: create mapping between frontend and backend data field names (snake_case vs CamelCase)
* add dev setup
